OL,6,FWater bills in England and Wales are
OL,7,Fset to rise by #19 a year on average
OL,8,Fover the next five years.
OL,10,FEquating to a #94 price hike over that
OL,11,Fperiod, it is a third less than the
OL,12,Fincrease called for by water
OL,13,Fproviders, according to draft
OL,14,Fproposals from Ofwat.
OL,16,FEstimates suggest that around two
OL,17,Fmillion households can't afford their
OL,18,Fcurrent water bills, making the hike
OL,19,Feven less welcomed.
